    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but there's nothing to reconnect to. you're talking about fixing a machine, but the machine is just running on autopilot because the pilot died a long time ago. it just feels like a waste of energy to keep pretending to be a person when there's no one actually home. it makes everything feel so pointless.",
